{"_id":"R3Wyao1bM85k4RKD","name":"Soulrend","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.R3Wyao1bM85k4RKD"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirements&nbsp;</strong>You are holding your shard weapon.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You imbue your shard weapon with the power to attack a creature's soul. Make a @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike}. If this strike hits, the target has to make a will save against your Class DC. <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">@Check[type:will|dc:resolve(@actor.attributes.classDC.value)]</span></p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Nothing happens.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target gains @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target gains @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> You reap the targets soul. It dies instantly.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Dullibrew"},"traits":{"value":["hb_shardbearer"],"rarity":"rare","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-26T00:44:11.039+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"level":{"value":6},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":2},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"ownership":{"default":0,"Mo4BbrN8EIUUVQ6C":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1666203436089,"lastModifiedBy":"jEnJa1KtZyjliOhd"}}
{"_id":"bV7dxWNDA6tFBVpI","name":"Shardcaller Dash","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.bV7dxWNDA6tFBVpI"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Requirements&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Your shard weapon is dismissed.</span></p>\n<hr>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">@Compendium[pf2e-dullibrew.dullibrew-actions.a5injyDf0U2zLmGi]{Recall Shard} while you </span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">@Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Bcxarzksqt9ezrs6]{Stride}. If you end your movement withing reach of atleast one enemy, you can make a @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} against that enemy.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">You can use Shardcaller Dash while Burrowing, Climbing, Flying, or Swimming instead of Striding if you have the corresponding movement type.</span></p>"},"source":{"value":"Dullibrew"},"traits":{"value":["hb_shardbearer"],"rarity":"uncommon","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-25T23:54:54.773+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"level":{"value":4},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":2},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"ownership":{"default":0,"Mo4BbrN8EIUUVQ6C":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1666203414038,"lastModifiedBy":"jEnJa1KtZyjliOhd"}}
{"_id":"boXGD8tCxaNbbe3u","name":"Sudden Block","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.he2uEwhxlHHUrEXu"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirements </strong>Your shard shield is dismissed. You have a free hand.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You would take damage from a physical attack.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You @Compendium[pf2e-dullibrew.dullibrew-actions.a5injyDf0U2zLmGi]{Recall your shard shield} and snap it in place to ward off a blow. Your shield prevents you from taking an amount of damage up to the shield's Hardness. You and the shield each take any remaining damage, possibly breaking or destroying the shield.</p>\n<p>If the attacking creatures uses vision as a precise sense it has to make a @Check[type:perception|dc:resolve(@actor.attributes.classDC.value)] against your Class DC.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The attacker is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Flat-Footed} for one round.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Dullibrew"},"traits":{"value":["hb_shardbearer"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-26T10:14:25.570+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"level":{"value":6},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Shield Bond"}]},"location":null},"ownership":{"default":0,"Mo4BbrN8EIUUVQ6C":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1666203442398,"lastModifiedBy":"jEnJa1KtZyjliOhd"}}
{"_id":"cv3f8B0umEDOjdYn","name":"Shardbearer Dedication","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.cv3f8B0umEDOjdYn"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You have learned the ability to forge a shard of yourself into a weapon. You learn a ritual that creates a magical bond between yourself and one weapon.</p>\n<p>You perform the ritual over the course of 1 hour. The weapon must be within your reach throughout the ritual, at the conclusion of which you touch the weapon and forge the bond.&nbsp;<br>Creating a bond with another weapon removes your bond with the previous weapon.</p>\n<p>Once you have bound a weapon to yourself, you can't be disarmed of that weapon unless you are incapacitated. <br>You can dismiss the bound weapon into a pocket dimenson using @Compendium[pf2e-dullibrew.dullibrew-actions.BXnryecr95kKU2Dz]{Dismiss Shard} and retrieve it with @Compendium[pf2e-dullibrew.dullibrew-actions.a5injyDf0U2zLmGi]{Recall Shard}.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Dullibrew"},"traits":{"value":["archetype","dedication"],"rarity":"rare","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-25T22:02:25.161+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"level":{"value":2},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Read atleast one book of the stormlight chronicles."}]},"location":null},"ownership":{"default":0,"Mo4BbrN8EIUUVQ6C":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1666203328029,"lastModifiedBy":"jEnJa1KtZyjliOhd"}}
{"_id":"pOVM1bhUMNMWaD13","name":"Shield Bond","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.xHrDxuCSALreC0oo"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can perform the binding ritual to additionally forge a shard of yourself into a shield.</p>\n<p>When the shard shield would be destroyed, it is dismissed into your pocket dimension instead and can't be recalled for 10 minutes.</p>\n<p>You can use @Compendium[pf2e-dullibrew.dullibrew-actions.BXnryecr95kKU2Dz]{Dismiss Shard} and @Compendium[pf2e-dullibrew.dullibrew-actions.a5injyDf0U2zLmGi]{Recall Shard} on your bound shield.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Dullibrew"},"traits":{"value":["hb_shardbearer"],"rarity":"uncommon","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Shield Block"}]},"location":null},"ownership":{"default":0,"jEnJa1KtZyjliOhd":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1666204112386,"modifiedTime":1666204250064,"lastModifiedBy":"jEnJa1KtZyjliOhd"}}
